DEXA Dual Energy Xray Absorptiometry, Bo.excld: Includes concepts that represent a diagnostic study of a dual-energy X-ray absorptiometry (DXA, DEXA) with 1 or more axial sites, axial skeleton (hips, pelvis, spine) or 1 or more appendicular skeleton sites (radius, wrist, heel).
